      • truthTP

        public MolecularSequence.Quality.Builder truthTP​(Decimal truthTP)
        True positives, from the perspective of the truth data, i.e. the number of sites in the Truth Call Set for which there are paths through the Query Call Set that are consistent with all of the alleles at this site, and for which there is an accurate genotype call for the event.
        Parameters:
        truthTP - True positives from the perspective of the truth data
        Returns:
        A reference to this Builder instance

      • queryTP

        public MolecularSequence.Quality.Builder queryTP​(Decimal queryTP)
        True positives, from the perspective of the query data, i.e. the number of sites in the Query Call Set for which there are paths through the Truth Call Set that are consistent with all of the alleles at this site, and for which there is an accurate genotype call for the event.
        Parameters:
        queryTP - True positives from the perspective of the query data
        Returns:
        A reference to this Builder instance

      • truthFN

        public MolecularSequence.Quality.Builder truthFN​(Decimal truthFN)
        False negatives, i.e. the number of sites in the Truth Call Set for which there is no path through the Query Call Set that is consistent with all of the alleles at this site, or sites for which there is an inaccurate genotype call for the event. Sites with correct variant but incorrect genotype are counted here.
        Parameters:
        truthFN - False negatives
        Returns:
        A reference to this Builder instance

      • queryFP

        public MolecularSequence.Quality.Builder queryFP​(Decimal queryFP)
        False positives, i.e. the number of sites in the Query Call Set for which there is no path through the Truth Call Set that is consistent with this site. Sites with correct variant but incorrect genotype are counted here.
        Parameters:
        queryFP - False positives
        Returns:
        A reference to this Builder instance

        Parameters:
        gtFP - False positives where the non-REF alleles in the Truth and Query Call Sets match
